data.title: A Global Initiative to Stop Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia
data.meta_description: CDH Support April is Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia Awareness Month! Starting April 1st, we will be celebrating CDH Awareness Month by displaying official CDH ribbons next to the names of cherubs on our website (www.CDHI.org) for the entire month. For a $5 donation, we will add another ribbon next to the name of your cherub! Donate
data.meta_site_name: CDH International - A Global Initiative to Stop Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia
data.text:
CDH Support

April is Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia Awareness Month!

April is Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia Awareness Month!

Join us as we work around the globe to raise awareness for Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia Awareness Month! And take action against CDH on April 19th, Congenital Diaphragmatic Hernia Action Day!!

Below are the names of children and adults born with CDH.

If you would like your cherub’s name edited or removed, please e-mail us. If you’d like your cherub listed, please join the charity for free and become an official member.
